            div#vizavail This system is based on open API, you can create new visualisation and integrate your analysis here. You'll be credited on this page, look for some ideas and to the current API set.

            table#listTable.display(cellspacing='0', width='100%')
                thead
                    tr
                        th When
                        th Precisely was...
                        th Last for
                        th Analyzed posts
                        th Total impressions
                tfoot
                    tr
                        th When
